=99s trauma response to ELC=E2=80=99s share prices dipping below $100 for t=
he first time since 2017. =E2=80=9CI think they were going to give him a ch=
ance to turn it around, but it was untenable,=E2=80=9D a former company exe=
cutive said. Another source close to the Lauder family remarked that they =
=E2=80=9Ccouldn=E2=80=99t get a fix on the revenue and profitability of the=
 company. There was no turnaround.=E2=80=9D The last straw, this person con=
tinued, was =E2=80=9Cwhen they were going to preview the earnings call and =
realized that next year was not going to make forecasts.=E2=80=9D <br/><br/=
>The timing of Freda=E2=80=99s exit came as a genuine shock inside the comp=
any. =E2=80=9CIt was much earlier than the company seemed to indicate just =
a few months ago, and that was a surprise,=E2=80=9D a person with ties to s=
enior leadership told me.
=E2=80=9CNo one knew it was coming,=E2=80=9D said the source close to the f=
amily. According to an Est=C3=A9e insider, the timeline might have been dif=
ferent had the company not been forced to lower its forecasts. =E2=80=9CThe=
y had no choice but to do it before the earnings in order to keep confidenc=
e that they were making changes,=E2=80=9D this person said, referring to Mo=
nday=E2=80=99s dismal quarterly call, when Lauder reported that net sales h=
ad dipped 2 percent from the previous year; that skin care and makeup reven=
ues declined by 3 percent and 1 percent, respectively; and warned that Chin=
a and travel retail continue to pose serious challenges to its business. <b=
r/><br/>Of course, there was never any doubt that Freda <i>would</i> be lea=
ving, at some point soon. This was the last official year of Freda=E2=80=99=
s current incentive package with the company, where he needed to remain C.E=
=2EO. until June 30, the end of Laud=
er=E2=80=99s fiscal 2024, to make his num=
bers. =E2=80=9CAt any other company, Fabrizio would have been gone
by now,=E2=80=9D a Lauder executive <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e=
